[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/hidden_power">Hidden Power</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>A variable move that's type and power depends on the IVs of the Pokemon using it.</p>